data.description: Fabulous location, charming yet spacious!  Built by a local builder featuring a covered porch, premium finishes throughout, hardwood floors on main level, granite countertops, ss appliances, and custom screened-in back porch with fireplace, makes for an ideal space for privacy or entertaining.  Enjoy the beautiful fenced in back yard with an outdoor fire pit for s'mores on those perfect fall evenings with friends. This location is convenient to shopping and dining; with quick commute access to Charlotte Pike, Briley Parkway, I-40, Rock Harbor Marina, West Nashville Shopping Center and Robertson Market, and downtown Broadway.
